====Spain====
Sexuality education in [[Spain]] is not a mandatory practice however upon a school deciding to instruct its students on the topic, educators rely heavily on outside [[health organizations]] and professionals to provide private workshops.{{sfn|SAFE|2006|pages=75–76}}

